== Game Modes ==

=== Action Mode ===
The main single-player puzzle mode.

'''Objective:'''
* Clear all cookies from the screen by forming complete rows and columns of matching cookie types

'''Mechanics:'''
* Move cursor with D-pad
* Press A to shift a row left/right or column up/down
* Complete rows/columns disappear
* New cookies fall from above
* Game ends when cookies reach the top

'''Speed Levels:'''
* Speed increases as rounds progress
* Higher rounds start with more cookies
* Bonus points for clearing multiple lines simultaneously

=== VS Mode ===
Two-player competitive mode.

'''Objective:'''
* Force opponent's screen to fill with cookies

'''Mechanics:'''
* Clearing multiple lines sends "garbage" cookies to opponent
* Yoshi cookies (special) can clear all of one type
* First player whose screen fills loses

=== Puzzle Mode ===
Pre-set puzzle challenges.

'''Objective:'''
* Clear all cookies with limited moves

'''Mechanics:'''
* Fixed starting positions
* Limited number of moves allowed
* Must clear all cookies to complete puzzle
* 100+ puzzles available

