== Clearing Mechanics ==

=== Row Clears ===
* Shift cookies in a row until all 5 match
* Row disappears when complete
* Points awarded based on cookie type and combo

=== Column Clears ===
* Shift cookies in a column until all match
* Column disappears when complete
* Adjacent clears trigger combos

=== Chain Reactions ===
* Clearing one line can cause falling cookies to form new matches
* Chain reactions multiply points
* Essential for high scores

=== Yoshi Cookie ===
* Special cookie appears periodically
* When used in a complete line, clears ALL cookies of that type
* Powerful for clearing screens quickly

