== Strategy Tips ==

'''Beginner:'''
* Focus on completing one line at a time
* Keep the screen as clear as possible
* Use Yoshi cookies on the most common cookie type

'''Intermediate:'''
* Set up multiple lines to clear simultaneously
* Plan two moves ahead
* Save Yoshi cookies for emergencies

'''Advanced:'''
* Create chain reaction setups
* Maximize combo potential before clearing
* In VS mode, time attacks to overwhelm opponent

